sor-- April 8th, 2003: The Patch that killed EverQue</span><hr size=1> I disagree completely...the &quot;old wheel&quot; didn't work either and was probably more &quot;broken&quot; than the changes that were currently made.  Having Rangers shoot unlimited arrows...often outdamaging Rogues, Monks and even wizards in some cases without any accoutability for their damage is &quot;broken&quot;.  Haveing enc's and mage's who's pets have a greater DPS than the entire party put together while the enc / mage never gains agro till charm breaks &quot;is broken&quot;.  Having clerics heal those pets and gain no agro &quot;is broken&quot;.  <br>
